%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">4.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">Peserta mampu memanipulasi dan mendokumentasi\r\nhasil kegiatan instansi dengan multimedia <span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;\">\r\n<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">POKOK BAHASAN<o:p></o:p></span></b></div>\r\n<div class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 18.0pt; margin-right: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm; mso-add-space: auto; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt;\">\r\n<!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"color: black; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Tehnik fotografi dokumentasi yang benar dalam acara fomal\r\npemerintah daerah</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" 